articles.title: South African pilot finds cobra under seat, makes emergency landing: "I kept looking down" - CBS News
articles.description: Rudolf Erasmus had four passengers on board when he felt "something cold" slide across his lower back
articles.content:
A pilot in South Africa made a hasty emergency landing after discovering a highly venomous cobra hiding under his seat.
